Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平心而论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, to put that in perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那相当于140年里每秒钟发生一次广岛爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that's about one Hiroshima-type blast...every second for about140 years.
