Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为奇克苏卢布撞击带来的后果\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What we think happened with the Chicxulub impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是会有较大的小行星闯入打击地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is you have a large asteroid coming in, it hits the Earth...
