Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以通过观察这个漂亮的水槽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We can learn about the effects that an asteroid impact...
