Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.20,0:41:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交织在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all going around together...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.00,0:41:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个可怜的小星系被撕碎后的残骸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that are the remnants of this poor little galaxy...that got ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.67,0:41:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系碰撞产生出数十亿颗恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Galaxy collisions produce billions of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.80,0:41:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而这些恒星也会碰撞吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but can these stars also collide?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.26,0:41:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们银河系里恒星之间的距离非常大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The space between stars in our galaxies is absolutely huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.76,0:41:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把太阳比作篮球那么大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf the Sun were about the size of a basketball...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.60,0:41:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在洛杉矶这里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and l'm here in Los Angeles...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.27,0:41:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么最近的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then the nearest star...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.56,0:41:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会是在纽约那里同样大小的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would be about the same-sized star in NewYork.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.86,0:41:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象成纽约的一个篮球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lmagine a basketball in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.94,0:41:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恒星之间有很大的距离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's so much space between stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.48,0:41:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 恒星的碰撞是相当罕见的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the stellar collisions are so rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.49,0:41:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管罕见 但是星际碰撞还是会在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Although rare, star collisions can occur...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.20,0:41:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密集的星团里时有发生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where stellar objects are formed in dense clusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.29,0:41:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们曾经见到过星团里的例子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've seen examples where in a cluster of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.88,0:41:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有恒星似乎天生就比其他星大很多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one star seems to be more massive than the other ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.88,0:41:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加年轻 旋转也快得多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}younger than the other ones, and spinning much faster...than the other stars that it was born with.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.85,0:42:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些年轻的恒星叫做蓝离散星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These young stars are called blue stragglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.73,0:42:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们所在罕见的致密星团称为球状星团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They occur in unusually dense groups of stars...called globular clusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.73,0:42:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们之所以称为蓝离散星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These are called blue stragglers...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.32,0:42:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为它们看似较为年轻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because they seem to be younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.36,0:42:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们相比星团里的其它恒星成长较慢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're aging less quickly than the other stars of the clusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.20,0:42:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 其极有可能是 两颗恒星合并而成的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it's very possible that these are caused...when two stars actually merge together.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.08,0:42:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这些恒星彼此接近时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As these stars approached each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.71,0:42:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会通过引力相互旋转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they spun each other up with their gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.75,0:42:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此你就会看到这个快速旋转的巨大亮星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and so you get this very fast-rotating, large, bright star.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.38,0:42:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恒星碰撞绝非轻微的星际小碰小擦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And star collisions are not mild galactic fender-benders.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.35,0:42:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会具有很大的破坏性\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They can be quite destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.18,0:42:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们会转得越来越靠近\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They would sort of loop closer and closer together...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.89,0:42:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转得越来越快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}going faster and faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.48,0:42:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的速度有可能达到时速数十万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They'd probably get to many hundreds of thousands...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.60,0:42:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至数百万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if not millions of miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.61,0:42:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在它们靠得很近时会相互撕扯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And they'd begin to rip bits of each other off...as they came close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.90,0:42:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此星际碰撞会是很有看头的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So a stellar collision could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.70,0:42:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极其戏剧性的暴力事件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an extremely dramatic, violent thing to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.16,0:43:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终 如果在足够的时间里有足够的物质转移\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eventually, if the mass transfer happens enough over enough time...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.08,0:43:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轨道就会收缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the orbits will shrink...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.08,0:43:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两颗恒星就会靠得越来越近\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and those two stars will get closer and closer together...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.46,0:43:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们最终会合并成一颗巨星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they could eventually merge...forming either one single giant star...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.59,0:43:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者最终塌缩成中子星 甚至黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or eventually collapsing into, say, a neutron star or a black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.30,0:43:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是恒星或星系的兼并\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whether they're star and galaxy mergers...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.97,0:43:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是小行星或彗星的碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or asteroid and comet impacts...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.64,0:43:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙碰撞还会继续发生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}cosmic collisions will continue to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.31,0:43:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要宇宙继续存在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as long as the universe exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.07,0:43:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过这些不可抗事件的知识的逐步积累\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By gaining knowledge about these uncontrollable events...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.44,0:43:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就可以达到更好地了解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we can reach a better understanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.49,0:43:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙的起源或许可以预测其未来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about the origins of the universe, and possibly predict its future.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.08,0:43:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙碰撞一直是塑造地球演化和历史的主要因素\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cosmic collisions have been a majorfactor...shaping the evolution and history of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.67,0:43:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有它们就不会有地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Earth wouldn't be here without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.75,0:44:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命起源所需的化学物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The chemicals that life needs to get started with...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.05,0:44:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是来自这些碰撞的过程\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}came out as a result of these impact processes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.80,0:44:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这其实一直是地球生命史上一个非常重要的因素\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This has actually been a very important factor...in the history of life on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.47,0:44:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙碰撞带来了形形色色的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cosmic collisions are responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.35,0:44:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如 小行星撞击\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for things as varied as asteroid impacts...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.56,0:44:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系兼并 巨星的形成\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}galaxy mergers, formation of giant stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.32,0:44:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们显然是我们了解宇宙现象的关键\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're obviously key to our understanding...of the phenomena in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.60,0:44:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thanks For Viewing
